            <p class="handbook-content-1 mt-2 mb-4">In Japan, visitors can visit large shopping centers such as Ginza, Asakusa, Shinjuku, etc. Here, visitors can shop for fashion brands such as Gucci, Chanel,..., modern technological equipment or souvenirs, traditional Japanese gifts such as human-shaped masks, embroidered paintings, paper paintings,... To be able to shop for the items you want, please refer to the article on famous shopping areas in Japan to guide your shopping plan when traveling to the land of the rising sun. .</p>


